{"title": "Essays, First Series", "description": "\u201cWe live in succession, in division, in parts, in particles. Meantime within man is the soul of the whole; the wise silence; the universal beauty, to which every part and particle is equally related, the eternal ONE. And this deep power in which we exist and whose beatitude is all accessible to us, is not only self-sufficing and perfect in every hour, but the act of seeing and the thing seen, the seer and the spectacle, the subject and the object, are one. We see the world piece by piece, as the sun, the moon, the animal, the tree; but the whole, of which these are shining parts, is the soul\u201d. (From Essay 9, \u2018The Over-Soul\u2019)", "duration": 30513, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "1159", "name": "Ralph Waldo Emerson"}], "coverArt": "https://www.archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt12/Essays_First_Series_1110.jpg", "copyright_year": "1841", "genres": ["Essays & Short Works"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "David Barnes"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "David Barnes"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Essay 01 - History", "readers": [102], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/essays_first_series_0708_librivox/essays_first_series_01_emerson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 3380}, {"section": 2, "title": "Essay 02 - Self-Reliance", "readers": [102], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/essays_first_series_0708_librivox/essays_first_series_02_emerson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 4032}, {"section": 3, "title": "Essay 03 - Compensation", "readers": [94], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/essays_first_series_0708_librivox/essays_first_series_03_emerson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 3384}, {"section": 4, "title": "Essay 04 - Spiritual Laws", "readers": [1096], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/essays_first_series_0708_librivox/essays_first_series_04_emerson_64kb.mp3", "duration": 3087}, {"section": 5, "title"